title: Kendall Jenner Lunches With Gigi Hadid & Cara Delevingne After Olivier Rousteing's Party
text: Kendall Jenner walks a little bit ahead of Gigi Hadid and Cara Delevingne after grabbing lunch together in Los Angeles on Saturday afternoon (October 24).
